  memoryId: document
  objectName: The Document
  objectSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 989fbf316a37340b998656b632cb787d, type: 3}
  glowSprite: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b9ecd1251fb1542239f39af529c037df, type: 3}
  shortDescription: A legal document. Medical Assistance in Dying request form.
    Locked behind three security questions.
  fullStory: "Robert locked it himself. Three questions, three secrets. His past
    self \u2014 driven by self-loathing \u2014 made sure he couldn\u2019t sign it
    without facing what he had done."
  marthaContext: Martha found the pamphlet three months ago. She hasn't brought it
    up. She won't. This has to be Robert's decision. She doesn't know about the
    security questions.
  davidContext: "David knows the document exists. He lost Margaret without choices.
    He will not take this one from Robert. But the questions must be answered first."
